{"tid":1001480,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"由細個笑d高登仔連登仔肥矮毒7冇女自己一個日日上網做毒L 到自己都變左佢地既一份子","createTime":"2019-01-30T07:41:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T07:56:32.000Z","uid":193492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c47c2b7ad365013933b2721c4e0c26b7867c56e9","tid":1001480,"uid":193492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T07:41:47.000Z","msg":"記得嗰陣中一（2011年左右）<br />\n對新開始既中學生生活 甚至係未來好有期盼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得自己會有個難忘既中學歲月 自己既青春同未來都會好開心有好多美好既回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有次朋友share d 高登音樂台既片比我睇<br />\n應該都係講d毒L搵唔到女朋友/收兵/lonely Christmas嗰類content<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰陣睇既時侯既反應係覺得好好笑 亦覺得唔會關自己事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n剩係覺得呢班人係失敗者 肯定冇我份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來中學過左 甚至之後上大學<br />\n中學自己都唔係出眾嗰班人 中庸 冇人留意（當然冇女啦）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上到大學 見到自己身邊既中同又上莊又剩 大把social life<br />\n個個都開始陸續出pool<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而自己都係一事無成 唔係太好又唔係太差咁過日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n先知原來自己而家已經都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e136e5c2bd6cdfbdfe935626e4b202d7b3402825","tid":1001480,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T07:42:57.000Z","msg":"死毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0a02c66b94afc8da47f032da9d818aca245c3c","tid":1001480,"uid":193492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e136e5c2bd6cdfbdfe935626e4b202d7b3402825","tid":1001480,"uid":201604,"like":0,"disl